items.title: Adani Power to cut power supply to Bangladesh if dues not settled by Nov 7: Report
items.description: In a prior letter to the Bangladesh Power Development Board (PDB), Adani Power had urged the clearance of outstanding dues by October 30.

items.title: Dr Reddy's recalls over 3.3 lakh bottles of generic medication in US: USFDA
items.description: New Jersey-based Dr Reddy’s Laboratories, Inc., a unit of Hyderabad-based drug major, is recalling 2,85,126 bottles of Cinacalcet tablets in 30 mg strength
